(8, '3592-01', 'Hedgerows Digital & Print Sales Centre', 'To create, prepare and install all print and digital solutions for the Hedgerows Sales information Centre.\n\nThe Digital installation will be completed on 24.10.2018 and the print installation on 26.10.2018\n\nThe Hedgerows development is located at: \n\nHedgerows,\nMooracre Lane,\nBolsover, \nS44 6ER\n\nPrint Requirements:\n\n4 x Graphic Boards - A1 portrait sized. Full colour, printed and laminated, drilled with 4 holes and with 19mm satin stand-offs\n\n1 x Graphic Board - A0 landscape sized. Full colour, printed and laminated, drilled with 4 holes and with 19mm satin stand-offs\n\n1 x Site Plan - A3 landscape sized for use under glass. Printed and laminated on 3mm PVC F/X board \n\n2x Brushed chrome “Welcome to Hegderows” lettering and Keepmoat Homes logo underneath - wall is 1800mm wide \n\n\nDigital Requirements:\n\n1x Kiosk: 10’’ tablet and unit mounted stand with white surround, flexible arm, lockable case and hosting \n\n16x My Colour Kitchen Product Symphony Bronze. Creation of the full house type range (16 kitchen layouts) \n\n1x 49’’ my display: Development video digital screen \n\n1x Development Video for Sales Centre digital screen & YouTube\n\n5x 32’’ my display: House type digital screens \n\n5x Video Graphic Board content formatted for the House Type digital screens', '2018-10-23', '2018-10-30', 8, '2018-10-24', 1, 'completed', '', 0, '', 0),
(9, '4209-00', 'Priory Meadows', 'A brand new housing development called Priory Meadows on Haggs Lane in Cartmel is being delivered by Applethwaite Homes in partnership with Holbeck Homes.\n\nWe are to create the following marketing assets (branded as Holbeck Homes):\n\n• 2D Master Site Plan (same style as the Brackenwood development)\n\n• 2 Street Scenes (plots 15-19 & 22-27)\n\n• 7 House Type CGI\'s:\n- D (plot 4)\n- E (plot 26)\n- F (plot 16)\n- G (plot 25)\n- H (plot 23)\n- J (plot 15)\n- L  (plot 5)\n\n• 7 House Type Floor Plans with dimensions and 2d furniture (minimal)\n\n• 1 minute development video with opening branded logo (above) and text showcasing the development\'s bedroom numbers. No call to action at the end just logo please fading in and out (camera work based on Lovell example saved on server)', '2019-01-14', '2019-05-07', 16, '2019-01-28', 7, 'open', 'BF', 0, '', 0),
