(21, '4210-02', 'Pendlebrook', 'To create an aerial view development video (Applethwaite Homes branded) based on previous project Priory Meadows (4209) and the Lovell\'s video in the reference folder.\n\nWe are to model the full site, materialise and render with new parked cars, variety of trees, minimal planting (i.e. pot plants / shrubs) hanging baskets (think over 55\'s), and a sun flare. Please also add in ghost houses for the surrounding areas.', '2019-02-28', '2019-05-03', 16, '2019-02-27', 7, 'open', '', 0, '', 0),
