(130, '4335', 'Trinity Gardens', 'Trinity Gardens, in Loughborough.\n\nNew development and our brief is:\n\n- Production of external CGI and floor plans for each house type (5 types). Marketing names to follow.\no R2 plot 197\no R2 SA plot 198\no R3 plot 177\no R3 SA plot 178\no ‘Didsbury Special’ - plot 155-156\n• 1 x street scene \n\nAlso creation of:\n- Site plan\n- ebrochure - 12 page digital brochure. No print required.\n\nPlanting Reference - M:\\Riverside Homes', '2019-04-17', '2019-04-30', 47, '2019-04-15', 11, 'open', '', 0, '', 0),
(131, '4336-00', 'Hot Tub Exterior Image', 'To create two marketing images to help sell the garden space of an apartment which is being privately rented. The garden space to the rear of the property is quaint and is being renovated from damaged paving flags to a modern grey decking for low maintenance. The owner is   installing a hot tub and gondola to create a space that\'s relaxing and sociable. \n\nWe are to create 2 x CGI\'s (both night shots):\n1 x full view looking towards the hot tub (see ref photo provided by client in ref other info folder)\n1 x creative view / low level close up (could be peering behind a lantern with depth of field)\n\nIdeas for the look and feel is a night shot, hot tub with steam and colour led, Gondola with curtains (open at the front), string lights in the top of the gondola and perhaps along the wall to the left with candle lanterns. To the right handside we could soften the space by adding in modern bamboo planting which will also cover the drainage pipes on the house. ', '2019-04-18', '2019-04-18', 42, '2019-04-17', 7, 'completed', 'TM', 0, '', 0),
